367
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,440
[when you left me.]

368
00:32:29,670 --> 00:32:31,590
[I've answered your question.]

369
00:32:31,670 --> 00:32:32,560
[What about you?]

370
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:34,080
I'm sorry.

371
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,840
You...

