in the music industry.

398
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,440
I won't spread it.

399
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:39,190
No problem for sure.

400
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:40,560
We've always wanted

401
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:41,350
