00:35:49,870 --> 00:35:51,070
Do you think I'll miss out on the chance?

431
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:53,760
You shouldn't do that.

432
00:35:54,720 --> 00:35:55,520
I know.

433
00:35:55,870 --> 00:35:57,350
My mum told me

434
00:35:57,590 --> 00:35:59,310
