525
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:04,240
You're still attending interviews?

526
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:06,830
Why did you leave before getting a job?

527
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:08,110
I thought...

528
00:41:08,190 --> 00:41:08,920
Or what?

529
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:11,350
