532
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:18,520
How was the interview?

533
00:41:19,830 --> 00:41:21,000
Don't ask.

534
00:41:21,080 --> 00:41:23,310
It's the ninth interview.

535
00:41:23,520 --> 00:41:25,200
