have high expectations for me.

544
00:41:44,870 --> 00:41:45,510
But I...

545
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:46,550
Stop it.

546
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:48,760
You make me sound like a counsellor.

547
00:41:51,350 --> 00:41:52,350
I get it.

548
00:41:53,350 --> 00:41:55,350
